content: I don't think so, seems like first steps are very clear. End goal is clear as well I believe. Looking for as close to singularity as we can get with the ability to override standard AI recommendations with personal experience and consolidated Thought Leader insights to serve the purpose of achieving the goals stated in the application, following the principles listed (or at least manual override required for exceptions to principles) as quickly as possible given my skills, experience and network. Does that sound accurate to you? And can you rephrase the mission of this in a manner that makes sense to both of us that will serve as guiding light for this project?
